Somizi never fails to dazzle on his reality show, and he once again had audiences in fits of laughter on Wednesday evening with tales of his glamorous life. The Idols judge was once again the hottest thing on the Twitter streets when he appeared on the show in his ash-white braids. It was all too much for fans who flooded Twitter with hilarious memes and jokes about the star’s hair. Perhaps one of the funniest moments on the show was when Somizi met with a local farmer to buy cattle to slaughter. Speaking of the experience, Somizi joked that whoever created English will never see heaven- and fans couldn't agree more. READ MORE: